org.apache.fluo.api.data

Class Column

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.fluo.api.data.Column
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Column>

    public final class Column
extends Object
implements Comparable<Column>, Serializable
    Represents all or a subset of the column family, column qualifier, and column visibility fields. A column with no fields set is represented by Column.EMPTY. Column is immutable after it is created.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
